      production»</em>.</ca>
  <es>Devuelve los registros que tengan como título exacto <em>«Higgs
      boson»</em> pero no registros como <em>«Overview of Higgs boson
      production»</em>.</es>
</lang>

<br/>(Note: For some indexes such as <em>any
field</em>, <em>title</em>, or <em>abstract</em>, there is no
distinction between searching for double quoted and single quoted
expressions.  Both behave the same usual way.)

